title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Oct 5 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Oct 5 2022
description:
Saudis tell Biden go pound sand, gas prices spike again. Clay says, "I think they figure, 'Hey, this guy is going to be a one-term president, let's screw him!'" Democrat Cori Bush defends defund the police. Clay says let's buy Cori Bush time on every network and just let her speak! Buck says they effectively already kicked the ball off on that by playing her ridiculous comment during the C&B show. DeSantis dunks on media, lead in the polls balloons to double-digits after exceptional hurricane response. Jesse Kelly rant on NYC tequila prices.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
